Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.04,0:24:31.27,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Did you know? Did you Know? Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.55,0:24:35.94,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,There's a baby koala in the eucalyptus tree
