Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.85,0:24:45.28,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,It gathers plenty of leaves to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.60,0:24:50.04,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,And naps in the cradle of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.04,0:25:04.26,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Did you know? Did you know? Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.54,0:25:08.97,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The kookaburra is playing by the river
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.29,0:25:13.64,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,It's always so merry, so merry
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.97,0:25:18.36,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Uhahahaha wuhahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.64,0:25:23.11,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Even if mischievous wuhahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.39,0:25:28.37,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to show you, I want to show you the forest animals
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.65,0:25:33.58,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to show them to you
